)Body  Expand(~~) window(73,09)
$ ~ ~ Cobal analyse reporting ~ ~
%Command   ===>_zcmd
%
#f1n       %===>|v1|f1                  #f1k                            +
#f2n       %===>|v2|f2                  #f2k                            +
#f3n       %===>|v3|f3                  #f3k                            +
%
%You can abbreviate any input value without '*'
)INIT
  .CURSOR = f1
  &zcmd   = &z
  if (&v1 = ' ') &v1 = EQ
  if (&f2n ¬= ' ')
     if (&v2= ' ') &v2 = EQ
  if (&f3n ¬= ' ')
     if (&v3= ' ') &v3 = EQ
)PROC
   VER (&V1,LIST,EQ,GT,GE,LT,LE,MSG=COBA003)
   VER (&V2,LIST,EQ,GT,GE,LT,LE,MSG=COBA003)
   VER (&V3,LIST,EQ,GT,GE,LT,LE,MSG=COBA003)
   VPUT (F1,F2,F3)
)END

$~ ~Cobol analyse reporting~ ~
%Command ===>_zcmd
%
+Loadlib   ==>#loadlib                                    +
+total pgm ==>¬anzpgmco+
+Cobol/VS  ==>¬anzcobvs+
+Cobol/2   ==>¬anzcobii+
+Cobol370  ==>¬anzcob37+
%
@1$= display all programs
@2$= display all COBOL/VS programs
@3$= display all COBOL/2  programs
@4$= display all COBOL370 programs
@5$= ISPF 3.4
)INIT
 .CURSOR         = zcmd
  &zcmd          = &z
 .attr(loadlib)  = 'color(turq) hilite(reverse)'
 .attr(anzpgmco) = 'color(yellow) hilite(reverse)'
 .attr(anzcobvs) = 'color(pink) hilite(reverse)'
 .attr(anzcobii) = 'color(pink) hilite(reverse)'
 .attr(anzcob37) = 'color(pink) hilite(reverse)'
)REINIT
 REFRESH(*)
)PROC
   VER (&ZCMD,LIST,1,2,3,4,5,
        ' ','TRACE',MSG=COBA002)
)PNTS
FIELD(ZPS00001) VAR(ZCMD) VAL(1)
FIELD(ZPS00002) VAR(ZCMD) VAL(2)
FIELD(ZPS00003) VAR(ZCMD) VAL(3)
FIELD(ZPS00004) VAR(ZCMD) VAL(4)
FIELD(ZPS00005) VAR(ZCMD) VAL(5)
)END
